OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPetrol deliveries: Visas   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffor foreign lorry drivers  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fextended                   
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Temporary visas are to be issued to 300
OL,6, overseas fuel drivers "immediately",   
OL,7, the government has announced.          
OL,9,FUnder the bespoke scheme, those foreign
OL,10,Fdrivers will be able to work in the UK 
OL,11,Ffrom now until the end of March.       
OL,13,FAdditionally, some 4,700 visas intended
OL,14,Ffor foreign food haulage drivers will  
OL,15,Fbe extended by two months, lasting from
OL,16,Flate October to the end of February.   
OL,18,FBut the government said temporary visas
OL,19,Fwere not a long-term solution and urged
OL,20,Ffirms to invest in a UK workforce.     
